      "acceptanceCriteria": "Code verification via method of manufactured solutions or equivalent for relevant equation sets.",
      "rationale": "Solver verified against analytical solutions for Poiseuille flow and rotating channel flow. Observed convergence rates match theoretical predictions for second-order spatial discretization."
