      "acceptanceCriteria": "Iterative convergence demonstrated to at least 4 decades reduction in residuals for all equations; round-off error assessed.",
      "rationale": "Residual convergence monitored but terminated at 2-3 decades reduction due to solver oscillations in the impeller passage at high rotational speeds. The team accepted this convergence level without demonstrating that QoIs were insensitive to further iteration. Round-off error was not assessed. Achieved level does not meet the required level for MRL 2 at High consequence."
