    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "The credibility assessment team determined that the overall simulation credibility is High based on the majority of factors meeting or exceeding required levels and the availability of direct experimental validation data for the FDA benchmark geometry. Factors with below-threshold achievement (discretization error, numerical solver error) were considered acceptable by the team given the availability of experimental validation. The model is accepted for use in identifying worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the Class II CPB device submission.",
